---
/**
 * rest-api/0009 · Figure 3 — "token bucket → 429 when empty": tokens refill at a
 * steady rate, each request spends one, and an empty bucket yields a 429 with
 * Retry-After plus the RateLimit-* headers sent on every response.
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from docs/rest-api/lessons/0009-error-design-rate-limiting-observability.html
 * (figure + svg + figcaption). Lives as an .astro component for the
 * kebab-case-SVG reason. Markers (#arw, #arwG, #arwR) come from the source's
 * global hidden <svg>, inlined here in a local <defs>, fills/ids verbatim.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 620 250"
        role="img"
        aria-label="A token bucket refills at a steady rate; each request spends one token; when the bucket is empty the server returns 429 with Retry-After and RateLimit headers"
    >
        <defs>
            <marker
                id="arw"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
                ><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#6b675f"></path></marker
            >
            <marker
                id="arwG"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
                ><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#2f5d3a"></path></marker
            >
            <marker
                id="arwR"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
                ><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#9a2417"></path></marker
            >
        </defs>
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <text
                x="310"
                y="18"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="12"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#111110">TOKEN BUCKET → 429 WHEN EMPTY</text
            >
            <!-- refill -->
            <text x="92" y="48" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" fill="#2f5d3a"
                >refill: steady rate</text
            >
            <line x1="92" y1="54" x2="92" y2="82" stroke="#2f5d3a" marker-end="url(#arwG)"></line>
            <!-- bucket -->
            <rect x="50" y="84" width="84" height="96" rx="6" fill="#fbfaf2" stroke="#6b675f"
            ></rect>
            <circle cx="72" cy="120" r="7" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"></circle>
            <circle cx="96" cy="120" r="7" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"></circle>
            <circle cx="120" cy="120" r="7" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"></circle>
            <circle cx="84" cy="142" r="7" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"></circle>
            <circle cx="108" cy="142" r="7" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"></circle>
            <text x="92" y="196" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >cap = burst size</text
            >
            <!-- spend one -->
            <line x1="134" y1="132" x2="186" y2="132" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"
            ></line>
            <text x="160" y="124" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >spend 1 / req</text
            >
            <!-- decision -->
            <rect x="190" y="100" width="120" height="64" rx="9" fill="#fff" stroke="#1f3a5a"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="250"
                y="128"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#1f3a5a">token left?</text
            >
            <text x="250" y="146" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >per principal</text
            >
            <!-- yes -->
            <path
                d="M 310 116 C 340 100, 360 96, 384 92"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#2f5d3a"
                marker-end="url(#arwG)"></path>
            <text x="352" y="92" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#2f5d3a">yes</text>
            <rect x="386" y="70" width="220" height="44" rx="9" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="496"
                y="90"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#2f5d3a">200 · served</text
            >
            <text x="496" y="105" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#244a2e"
                >RateLimit-Remaining decremented</text
            >
            <!-- no -->
            <path
                d="M 310 150 C 340 166, 360 172, 384 178"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#9a2417"
                marker-end="url(#arwR)"></path>
            <text x="352" y="178" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#9a2417">empty</text>
            <rect x="386" y="150" width="220" height="76" rx="9" fill="#f7ecea" stroke="#9a2417"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="496"
                y="170"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#9a2417">429 Too Many Requests</text
            >
            <text
                x="496"
                y="188"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="9"
                font-family="ui-monospace,monospace"
                fill="#7a2218">Retry-After: 30</text
            >
            <text
                x="496"
                y="204"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="9"
                font-family="ui-monospace,monospace"
                fill="#7a2218">RateLimit-Limit / -Remaining / -Reset</text
            >
            <text x="496" y="219" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
                >headers sent on EVERY response</text
            >
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        Tokens refill steadily; a burst drains the cap, then it's steady-state. Empty bucket → <code
            >429</code
        > + <code>Retry-After</code>, so good clients back off on their own.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
